{
  "stem": "747.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No water, so-- and it was just-- in the air, it was flying, just-- you know, it was-- everything was black.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was flying from the-- out from the chimney, this-- I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was soot?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What, what was it?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Soot.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soot.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Human flesh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Yup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the clothes, what we got.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We never knew that who wore it last.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The shoes what I put on belonged to someone before me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My number belonged to someone before me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it was-- we were just replacements.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, what happened-- you can check it out, but I was told-- and then I just-- you know everything was through the grapevine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When someone was killed with this number, they had, they had a file.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Red Cross came from time to time to, to check it out, what everything looks-- and it never looked orderly because we marched out in the same uniform, kerchief.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't see that we have no hair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a bowl under our arm, marching five in a row, singing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It looked everything fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they looked in the files and they saw a number of people working.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that number didn't exactly belong to that person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That, nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, the Red Cross certainly didn't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So then somebody, Mengele, sent walking, and the following day, they gave that number for someone else.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People were not missing, obviously, someone else came who could fill their shoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were a non-person, no name, just a number.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How many years have you been married?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, '46.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How many that makes it? 48.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have a son and a daughter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they're good children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm very grateful.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
